additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Keep out of reach of children. Irritant. Avoid contact with skin & eyes. Contains Alkaline Salts. Not to be consumed. If swallowed do not induce vomiting. Drink a glass of water. Contact a doctor or Poisons Information Centre (13 11 26). If in the eyes, hold open, flush eye with water for at least 15 minutes and consult a doctor.
